trans-unit.source: Implementation of itertools, builtins, and more for AsyncIO and mixed-type iterables.
trans-unit.target: 实现AsyncIO和混合型迭代器的itertools、buildins等。

trans-unit.source: See builtins.py, itertools.py, and more_itertools.py for full documentation of functions and abilities.
trans-unit.target: 见builtins.py，itertools.py和more_itertools.py的功能和能力的完整文档。

trans-unit.source: aioitertools emulates the entire itertools module, offering the same function signatures, but as async generators. All functions support standard iterables and async iterables alike, and can take functions or coroutines:
trans-unit.target: aioitertools模拟整个 itertools 模块，提供相同的功能签名，但作为异步生成器。所有函数都支持标准可迭代和异步可迭代，并且可以采用函数或协程：

trans-unit.source: aioitertools requires Python 3.6 or newer. You can install it from PyPI:
trans-unit.target: aioitertools 需要 Python 3.6 或更新版本。你可以从PyPI安装它。

trans-unit.source: aioitertools shadows the standard library whenever possible to provide asynchronous version of the modules and functions you already know. It's fully compatible with standard iterators and async iterators alike, giving you one unified, familiar interface for interacting with iterable objects:
trans-unit.target: 只要有可能，aioitertools都会隐藏标准库，以提供您已经知道的模块和功能的异步版本。它与标准迭代器和异步迭代器完全兼容，从而为您提供了一个统一的，熟悉的界面来与可迭代对象进行交互：

trans-unit.source: itertools and builtins for AsyncIO and mixed iterables
trans-unit.target: 用于AsyncIO和混合iterables的itertools和内建模块。
